code: public String filename(String version) {     String architecture = "".     if (version.startsWith("6.") == false) {         if (packaging == Packaging.DEB) {             architecture = "-amd64".         } else {             if (packaging != Packaging.RPM) {                 architecture = "-" + platform.toString().             }             architecture += "-x86_64".         }     }     return flavor.name + "-" + version + architecture + packaging.extension. }
